URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.wnpld.org/event/americas-most-unusual-festivals-3
 7055
STATUS:CANCELLED
CREATED:20251203T185622Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260306T195318Z
DESCRIPTION:Join multi-Emmy Award winning producer and editor Harvey Moshma
 n for a screening of a 1-hour special of the PBS series Wild Travels. Whet
 her you’re inspired to walk by the STAND STILL PARADE in Whalan\, Minnes
 ota or enter your facial hair in the INTERNATIONAL BEARD & MUSTACHE COMPET
 ITION in Portland\, Oregon (ladies welcome!)\, AMERICA'S MOST UNUSUAL FEST
 IVALS is your VIP pass to the craziest annual celebrations that the US of 
 A has to offer. Screening followed by live Q&A.This presentation is CANCEL
 LED for March 15\, 2026. It is rescheduled for March 29th\, 2026.
CATEGORIES:History,Other
