BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:32944
DTSTAMP:20260314T214529Z
SUMMARY:The Founding Mothers with Laura Keyes
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.wnpld.org/event/founding-mothers-laura-keyes-3294
 4
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20250818T155121Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260202T224159Z
DESCRIPTION:The “Mothers” of America aren’t often mentioned – the w
 omen whose influence on the early years of the United States reverberated 
 for centuries afterwards. This illustrated lecture will show the important
  role women played in the founding of our country. Learn about soldiers\, 
 writers\, printers\, scholars\, farmers and spies-all women and all vital 
 to our nation's history.
CATEGORIES:History
DTSTART:20260318T000000Z
DTEND:20260318T013000Z
LOCATION:US
END:VEVENT
