STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251125T222622Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260211T161501Z
DESCRIPTION:Before his death\, Houdini stated that should it be possible to
  contact the living from the other side\, he would do so. The question rem
 ains as to whether or not he actually succeeded…Join Troy Taylor on what
  would have been Houdini's 152nd birthday (100 years after his death) to l
 earn about this American enigma's life\, and possible afterlife.
CATEGORIES:History
