BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:35322
DTSTAMP:20260314T214529Z
SUMMARY:Lee & Grant at Appomattox Court House: A Day of Reckoning
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.wnpld.org/event/illinois-history-program-tbd-3532
 2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251022T215855Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260211T161514Z
DESCRIPTION:In the final days of the American Civil War\, two men both trai
 ned in the art of war but from vastly different backgrounds would come tog
 ether to begin the process of ending the conflict and returning the nation
  to peace.  What would come out of those meetings would not only set the 
 tone for how other armies still in the fight would transition from war to 
 peace but also how the nation would move forward from the bloodiest confli
 ct in American History.
CATEGORIES:History
DTSTART:20260403T000000Z
DTEND:20260403T010000Z
LOCATION:US
END:VEVENT
