BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:38200
DTSTAMP:20260314T214529Z
SUMMARY:Sorting It Out: Understanding Winnetka's New Waste and Recycling To
 ols
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.wnpld.org/event/sorting-it-out-38200
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251230T204521Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260207T220243Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a waste-related presentation highlighting programmi
 ng changes in Winnetka\, including the introduction of the Recycle Coach a
 pp\, the Hefty ReNew curbside collection for hard-to-recycle soft plastics
 \, and the sunsetting of the polystyrene drop-off collection at Winnetka P
 ublic Works. Christina Seibert\, Executive Director of the Solid Waste Age
 ncy of Northern Cook County\, and Elyse Steiner\, Sustainability Coordinat
 or for the Village of Winnetka\, will co-present with Liz Kunkle of Go Gre
 en Winnetka and Recycle Coach. This event is sponsored by Go Green Winnet
 ka.
CATEGORIES:Other
DTSTART:20260416T000000Z
DTEND:20260416T010000Z
LOCATION:768 Oak Street\, Winnetka\, IL\, 60093\, US
ROOM:Lloyd Room
GEO:42.1043086;-87.732896
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:35987
DTSTAMP:20260314T214529Z
SUMMARY:The History of Billy Joel
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.wnpld.org/event/history-billy-joel-35987
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251113T224002Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260211T161533Z
DESCRIPTION:Though Billy Joel has not released a new rock album in over 27 
 years\, he remains one of the world’s most popular live performers.  Us
 ing performance and interview video clips we’ll trace the arc of Billy
 ’s career from his humble beginnings in Hicksville\, NY to his slow rise
  to fame and his long string of hits including “Just The Way You Are”\
 , ”It’s Still Rock N Roll To Me”\, ”Uptown Girl” and “River Of
  Dreams” to his love life including his marriage to supermodel Christie 
 Brinkley and finally to his current status as one of the world’s most su
 ccessful touring acts.  “If you’re in the mood for a melody…the Pia
 no Man will make you feel alright.”
CATEGORIES:History,Other
DTSTART:20260416T000000Z
DTEND:20260416T010000Z
LOCATION:US
END:VEVENT
