BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:31376
DTSTAMP:20260314T214529Z
SUMMARY:James Madison: Father of the US Constitution with Terry Lynch
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.wnpld.org/event/james-madison-father-us-constitut
 ion-terry-lynch-backup-reservation-31376
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20250711T150759Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260211T161543Z
DESCRIPTION:Join actor Terry Lynch in his spirited portrayal of James Madis
 on\, who was famously known as our fourth president and the "Father of the
  U.S. Constitution". Small in stature\, but big in determination\, he co-a
 uthored the Federalist Papers\, which were instrumental in explaining the 
 need for a strong central government\, and promoted the U.S. Constitution 
 as the best model for that government.
CATEGORIES:Live Performance
DTSTART:20260418T200000Z
DTEND:20260418T210000Z
LOCATION:768 Oak Street\, Winnetka\, IL\, 60093\, US
ROOM:Lloyd Room
GEO:42.1043086;-87.732896
END:VEVENT
