BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:35494
DTSTAMP:20260314T214529Z
SUMMARY:Retirement Reality with Jill Schlesinger
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.wnpld.org/event/retirement-reality-jill-schlesing
 er-35494
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251029T212806Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260303T160446Z
DESCRIPTION:Are you thinking about retirement? Does it seem completely out 
 of reach? Emmy Award and Gracie Award Winning Business Analyst for CBS New
 s Jill Schlesinger\, CFP\, will join us to walk through the specific steps
  necessary to get you where you want to go\, whether you are just starting
  off in your career or ready to wind down. Join us as Jill takes the myste
 ry out of your finances and helps you take control.This is one of a collab
 orative series of virtual events presented by BIG (Business Interest Group
 ) and co-sponsored by 23 public libraries in the Chicago area for Financia
 l Fitness 2026.Register for this webinar here:https://us02web.zoom.us/webi
 nar/register/WN_lbWWultASeWQ8u0oG-cuVg
CATEGORIES:Personal Finance
DTSTART:20260422T000000Z
DTEND:20260422T013000Z
LOCATION:US
END:VEVENT
