BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:38008
DTSTAMP:20260314T214529Z
SUMMARY:Spring Migration Birding Walk
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.wnpld.org/event/spring-migration-birding-walk-380
 08
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251222T224528Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260211T161621Z
DESCRIPTION:Join Red Hill Birding's founder Josh Engel at the Skokie Lagoon
 s to learn about bird migration and see spring migrants at one of our best
  local birding hotspots. The beginning of April is a transitional period w
 hen a wide variety of species are passing through on their way north\, res
 ulting in high bird diversity and a large number of birds. Our walk will b
 e easy\, slow-paced\, and educational\, and hopefully we will see lots of 
 birds! Bring binoculars if you have them\, but if you don't\, that's no pr
 oblem.Please meet us at the north end of the parking lot off of Willow Roa
 d here:https://maps.app.goo.gl/W1EAkqmLoonUWQyY6
CATEGORIES:Other
DTSTART:20260509T150000Z
DTEND:20260509T163000Z
LOCATION:Skokie Lagoons\, Winnetka\, IL\, 60093\, US
GEO:42.103583333333;-87.76625
END:VEVENT
